{"type": "article", "id": 38494, "title": "盆栽难种？这里有个金属版本其实也挺好看｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-06T23:28:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 16955, "name": "Palomar"}, {"id": 38275, "name": "Ding3000"}, {"id": 38276, "name": "RockPaperRobot"}, {"id": 38277, "name": "SLUGHAUS"}, {"id": 38278, "name": "Matthew Gollop"}, {"id": 38279, "name": "Iwona Przybyla"}, {"id": 38280, "name": "Sean Avery"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 106, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170306211644i1payRfS7DtFTBHm.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Metal Bonsai by Matthew Gollop</h3><p>喜欢盆栽却担心自己照顾不周？不妨来看看英国艺术家用金属线制作的金属盆栽系列。这种特别的创作形式其实源于 Gollop 的一次弄巧成拙：在他摆弄一瓶香槟的铁丝封口时，无意间把它塑造成了一棵树的模样。根据不同的盆栽种类，所要用到的金属线长度也各不相同，最长需要将近 1.5 米。为了让它们显得更加逼真，Gollop 还会搭配专用的花盆。你可以通过<a href=\"http://metalbonsai.com/\">官方网站</a>购买到这些盆栽，售价从 19 到 249 英镑不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211734mVRt8qWrlFP05G9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211734V8IxGb2fDqjZhTuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211734ahRWExT2JOVF3yuf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211735mnFJvAlG1NjKOWZI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703062117350ygdzcxeCZBkjE6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ollie Chair by RockPaperRobot</h3><p>谁说折叠椅不能带给人一点惊喜？由纽约设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.rockpaperrobot.com/\">RockPaperRobot</a> 制作的 Ollie 是一把可以轻松地在平面和立体状态间切换的折叠椅。在不使用的时候，Ollie 可以收纳成一张由木条构成的木帘，仅厚 5.7 厘米的它不仅节约了空间，你还可以在上面涂鸦并通过背面的镂空挂上墙用作装饰。和常见的折叠椅相比，Ollie 另一个优势在于它独特的弧度，设计团队为此邀请了各种体型的人试坐，以得出保护腰部的曲线。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/144629748/the-ollie-chair-shape-shifting-seating\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 300 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703062117515TC9VAE7OlwoN1Gh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676471\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211750jOeUo85aB2drwJmn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.351471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211751ptH5kPzdZQmuM0Bj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.136765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703062117509fLXBJOQ0d6zlMHY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211750ave395cmkAMWdYSz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BULLET 02 by SLUGHAUS</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.slughaus.com/\">SLUGHAUS</a> 是美国旧金山的一间设计公司，致力于开发实用且美观的日用工具。他们曾在去年初推出了号称世界上最小的 LED 手电筒 BULLET，如名字所指，它的造型正是借鉴了经典的 40 S&amp;W 子弹。一年后，SLUGHAUS 带来了不仅更小而且具有防水功能的迭代款。根据团队的测试，亮起时将它浸在水下长达 5 分钟也不会有水渗入。对于参与户外活动的人来说，不失为一个便捷的照明工具备选。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bullet/bullet-02-worlds-smallest-flashlight-even-smaller\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 10 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211836t7yRgxbMvoU4Kncp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211836rYZoixCSWpbzF7Il.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211835xvGcOelIuJrs78H2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703062118362rxRcfehq95gAE8W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Monkey by Ding3000</h3><p>作为一款便携式音乐播放器，德国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.ding3000.com/\">Ding3000</a> 为意大利创意产品公司 <a href=\"https://www.palomarweb.com/\">Palomar</a> 设计的 Monkey 会让你感受到同名小动物所具有的活泼感。它最大的特点在于由弹簧钢制成的“尾巴”，既可以当做挂绳，又能作为收音机的天线使用。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.palomarweb.com/product/themonkey/\">订购链接</a>，售价为 69 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211911yx6zJHwX8h7iKsD1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211911gRUO2E1BWvd0kiQF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211911RInJEwpHlDu9dTMy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211911745SuFj3IMzdTQiK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>North Ice by Iwona Przybyla</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/47098997/NORTH-ICE\">North Ice</a> 是波兰平面设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/Iwona_Przybyla\">Iwona Przybyla</a> 以北欧为主题设计的一款护肤品概念包装。为了体现出产品纯净的特质，Przybyla 特意将白色的纸盒打造成了不规则的立方体，让人联想到了北方的冰川。在信息的呈现上也秉持了极简、克制的处理，仅出现了产品的 logo 。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211931B4Eh9CXGo6Vxuzgf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211931KqQOfL7BVltvcW3H.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211931OtSpPuDaENX5QWRi.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703062119322DcRKvXjBNYGOuFy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211932zT8buAwk1xYneLaF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211933cTOoMqQ4D1Inisdu.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>CD Animal Sculpture by Sean Avery</h3><p>谁说 CD 坏了只能丢进垃圾桶？现居澳大利亚珀斯的南非裔艺术家 <a href=\"http://seaneavery.com/home.html\">Sean Avery</a> 从这些废弃物中发现了另一种可能。为了完成这些动物雕塑，Avery 在搜集原材料的阶段就花费了大量时间，然后再根据需要将 CD 裁成碎片，黏在塑形用的铁丝框架外，碎片本身的光泽让他无需在颜色上对它们进行额外的处理。不过因为材料稀缺，Avery 完成的雕塑数量相当有限。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211950DaPo652REm1gCkc0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563077\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211951aWB8rKFuRMY69qLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.029231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211951rn9lxeC3WwkyifZm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.980000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211950S2zZniYqEhGQW45x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170306211951EVaDq9NLFAKxd3hQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.861538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}